{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, ChatGPT has been found to generate non-existent references to support its output [138,139].",
    "This tendency affects the trustworthiness of AI-generated data, raising serious concerns regarding its application in medical education.",
    "ChatGPT's uneven replies to identical cues add to its reliability issues [140].",
    "Another limitation of generative AI models such as ChatGPT-4 is its lack of direct access to real-time information [141].",
    "For example, GPT-3.5 was trained on data till September 2021, while ChatGPT-4 has training data until March 2023 [142]."
  ]
}